The paper discusses the development of efficient data structures for storing, processing, indexing, searching, and navigating genome-scale data, which is a common problem in computer science subfields such as data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), bioinformatics (cs.BIO), databases (cs.DB), and computational engineering (cs.CE).
